{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"jdq1espvg8fvmtupqfrhdg1","title":"Text","desc":"","updated":1658539079620,"created":1658327154392,"custom":{},"fname":"reference.ui-design.text","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","name":"digital-garden","selfContained":true},"contentHash":"58586a282e312a97aff90ccc27b22464","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"reference.ui-design.text","id":"jdq1espvg8fvmtupqfrhdg1","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"reference.tools-for.finding-font-pairings","alias":"Tools for Finding Font Pairings","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":3,"offset":99},"end":{"line":6,"column":80,"offset":176},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"reference.tools-for.finding-font-pairings"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"reference.ui-design.text","id":"jdq1espvg8fvmtupqfrhdg1","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"reference.tools-for.finding-font-sizes","alias":"Tools for Finding Font Sizes","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":3,"offset":297},"end":{"line":10,"column":74,"offset":368},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"reference.tools-for.finding-font-sizes"}},{"type":"ref","from":{"fname":"reference.ui-design.text","id":"jdq1espvg8fvmtupqfrhdg1","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"reference.ui-design","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":790},"end":{"line":22,"column":40,"offset":827},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"reference.ui-design","anchorHeader":"alignment:#*"}},{"from":{"fname":"reference.ui-design","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":3,"offset":349},"end":{"line":13,"column":31,"offset":377},"indent":[]},"value":"reference.ui-design.text","alias":"reference.ui-design.text"}],"anchors":{"text":{"type":"header","text":"Text","value":"text","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"use-great-fonts":{"type":"header","text":"Use great fonts","value":"use-great-fonts","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2},"font-size":{"type":"header","text":"Font Size","value":"font-size","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"line-length":{"type":"header","text":"Line length","value":"line-length","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2},"use-more-uppercase":{"type":"header","text":"Use more Uppercase","value":"use-more-uppercase","line":24,"column":0,"depth":2},"text-on-images":{"type":"header","text":"Text on Images","value":"text-on-images","line":32,"column":0,"depth":2},"font-recommendations":{"type":"header","text":"Font Recommendations","value":"font-recommendations","line":44,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"8ibsbx74seaqalt8quejc2g","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"text\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#text\"></a>Text</h1>\n<h2 id=\"use-great-fonts\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#use-great-fonts\"></a>Use great fonts</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Check the fonts of great designs</li>\n<li>Have a collection of great fonts</li>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/5di5kvensezvok1cbaedws6\">Tools for Finding Font Pairings</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"font-size\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#font-size\"></a>Font Size</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Not all font sizes work together well, use the calculator below to find sizes that work well together</li>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/40tilj5moa78uv2akteyhmz\">Tools for Finding Font Sizes</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"line-length\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#line-length\"></a>Line length</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>One line should be between 45-75 characters ideally.</li>\n<li>Adjust text column width to fit that</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Source:</strong> Design Academy - Debugging Design: Rejigging Layouts</p>\n<h2 id=\"use-more-uppercase\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#use-more-uppercase\"></a>Use more Uppercase</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Feel free to use uppercase text in short text elements like menus, headlines, button labels</li>\n<li>It draws attention to those things</li>\n<li>It gives a bigger sense of alignment (i.e. that something was designed with intention)\n<p></p><div class=\"portal-container\">\n<div class=\"portal-head\">\n<div class=\"portal-backlink\">\n<div class=\"portal-title\">From <span class=\"portal-text-title\">UI Design</span></div>\n<a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/8ibsbx74seaqalt8quejc2g\" class=\"portal-arrow\">Go to text <span class=\"right-arrow\">→</span></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"portal-parent-anchor\" class=\"portal-parent\" markdown=\"1\">\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-top\"></div>\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-bottom\"></div><h2 id=\"alignment\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#alignment\"></a>Alignment</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Design = Alignment</li>\n<li>You don't have to use a single line but still things are aligned to each other</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/digital-garden/assets/images/alignment-example.png\" alt=\"Alignment example\"></p>\n</div></div><p></p></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Source:</strong> Design Hacks - The easiest design tip (no one EVER teaches this 🤦‍♂️)</p>\n<h2 id=\"text-on-images\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#text-on-images\"></a>Text on Images</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Text on images usually looks good!</li>\n<li>But if the image could be anything (like an user-uploaded profile picture), readability can be a problem</li>\n<li>Some solutions:\n<ul>\n<li>Use a dark box around the text</li>\n<li>Floor Fade - Use a black gradient on the bottom of the picture</li>\n<li>Tint the whole picture</li>\n<li>Text shadow (sometimes unreliable)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Source:</strong> Design Hacks - Why I’m jealous of graphic designers</p>\n<h2 id=\"font-recommendations\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#font-recommendations\"></a>Font Recommendations</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Fira Sans: clean/simple with a side of warmth/humanity</li>\n<li>Inter: Un-opinionated and readable. If I found myself thinking “Man, I really want to use Helvetica here”,</li>\n<li>Clear Sans\n<ul>\n<li>squared-off feel, brands that are data-driven, scientific, masculine, or authoritative</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Source Sans Pro\n<ul>\n<li>neutral character, just a touch of humanist warmth, works great for user interfaces</li>\n<li>Has partner fonts: Source Serif, Source Code Pro (monospace) - but stands well on its own</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>PT Serif: more formal, knowledgeable, academic, official, or authoritative settings</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/8ibsbx74seaqalt8quejc2g\">UI Design</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","title":"Home","desc":"","updated":1655543408062,"created":1648806032875,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","name":"digital-garden","selfContained":true},"contentHash":"85274ee61d0bc9adc52197cbfa78a37d","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"contact_me","alias":"contact_me","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":55,"offset":331},"end":{"line":10,"column":69,"offset":345},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"contact_me"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"areas.gamedev","alias":"areas.gamedev","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":3,"offset":389},"end":{"line":14,"column":20,"offset":406},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"areas.gamedev"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"areas.software-development","alias":"areas.software-development","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":3,"offset":409},"end":{"line":15,"column":33,"offset":439},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"areas.software-development"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"reference.faith-and-work","alias":"reference.faith-and-work","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":3,"offset":442},"end":{"line":16,"column":31,"offset":470},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"reference.faith-and-work"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"reference.spiritual-abuse","alias":"reference.spiritual-abuse","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":3,"offset":480},"end":{"line":18,"column":32,"offset":509},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"reference.spiritual-abuse"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"areas.pkm","alias":"Personal Knowledge Management (PKM)","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":3,"offset":524},"end":{"line":19,"column":52,"offset":573},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"areas.pkm"}}],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-little-corner-of-the-internet":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my little corner of the internet","value":"welcome-to-my-little-corner-of-the-internet","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"topics":{"type":"header","text":"Topics","value":"topics","line":19,"column":0,"depth":2},"interests":{"type":"header","text":"Interests","value":"interests","line":28,"column":0,"depth":2},"media-i-enjoy":{"type":"header","text":"Media I enjoy","value":"media-i-enjoy","line":34,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["ckpt5dqzm4fv2ysnyyqi5q7","qexkgwym6yebjwrl1pz2wco","contact_me","gk4xjszil72ursnl10ui5ht","tu102fn6psvc3ef33p2jl5p","426vv89cwpwrk3pezm4idax","43bj5hyl41q0txr2e0rhcaw","xvvzpakah5wmytby6yncvwo","s2najqf438p0efaqmajbj9g","sdxhyjnqnw5wo259y2xkoia","7apeos526o1arxjgf2of7nd"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my little corner of the internet\n\nHey, everyone!\n\nI'm Kevin and this page is my own shot at a Digital Garden[^1].\n\nThis is a low-barrier[^2] experiment for myself to organize my thoughts and publish content and maybe find like-minded\nindividuals to connect with.\n\nThis space will slowly evolve over time. Feel free to [[contact_me]] if you want to get in touch.\n\n\n## Topics\n- [[areas.gamedev]]\n- [[areas.software-development]]\n- [[reference.faith-and-work]]\n- ADHD\n- [[reference.spiritual-abuse]] in churches\n- [[Personal Knowledge Management (PKM)|areas.pkm]]\n\n\n## Interests\n\n- Christian faith and Creativity/Art/Media\n- Communicating the Christian faith in foreign cultures (especially in Asia & Japan)\n- Machine Learning\n\n## Media I enjoy\n- 🇯🇵 Anime/Manga\n  - Steins;Gate\n  - Attack on Titan\n  - Death Note\n- 📺 TV Series\n  - Twelve Monkeys\n  - Dark\n  - Deep Space 9\n- 🎥 Movies\n  - Big Fish\n  - Memento\n- 📖 Books\n  - Das Haus der Geschichten (Thomas Franke)\n  - The Screwtape Letters (C.S. Lewis)\n- 🎮 Video Games\n  - Secret of Mana (SNES)\n  - Outer Wilds\n  - Undertale\n\n\n[^1]: I recommend the explanation on [Joschua's Garden](https://joschuasgarden.com/Digital+garden) and his digital garden in general.\n\n[^2]: I personally thought several times about starting a blog for sharing game development, software engineering tidbits/ramblings but my tendency for perfectionism especially with regard to minor details like names, design, style as well as the perceived pressure of having to regularly output some kind of meaningful content stopped me from actually going through with it until now.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":"<link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/atom+xml\" href=\"https://kfischer-okarin.github.io/digital-garden/feed.xml\">\n","config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":true,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNote":{"in